    public static enum Arithmetics.Axis
extends java.lang.Enum<Arithmetics.Axis>
    Contains all axes on which the tabs of a TabSwitcher can be moved.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      DRAGGING_AXIS
      The axis on which a tab is moved when dragging it.
      ORTHOGONAL_AXIS
      The axis on which a tab is moved, when it is added to or removed from the switcher.
      X_AXIS
      The horizontal axis.
      Y_AXIS
      The vertical axis.
